  "title": "Murder She Improvised",
  "description": "It's the International mystery sensation Murder, She Improvised, the murdery whodunit where the killer truly is TBD! A heinous crime will be committed before your very eyes and our detective will have only their wits and the audiences' deeply unhelpful suggestions to assist them in solving the case.",
  "credits": "<strong>Director</strong>: Matt Horgan<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: A rotating cast of the finest improvisers from across the Fringe Festival, including players from Rapid Fire Theatre, Dad's Garage Theatre Company, Gordon's Big Bald Head and more!<br/>",
  "website": "https://rapidfiretheatre.com",
  "plain_language": "This is a funny mystery show where someone (pretend) gets murdered, and a detective tries to solve the case. The audience writes down silly ideas to help, but they usually just make things harder! The detective has to figure it out using both their brain and the goofy clues. The killer is a surprise until the very end!",
